title: Preito e Homenagem
body: A single issue of a newspaper that was published in July 1908, in homage to the deceased priest Ernesto Schmitz. His Excellency the military honors due to him.

Ernesto Schmitz: Deceased priest in whose honor the single issue of the newspaper was published in July 1908.

1908: Year in which the single issue of the newspaper was published in honor of the priest Ernesto Schmitz.
